{% comment %}
  Recharge Affinity Customer Portal — Homepage "Next Order" Card Reskin
  =====================================================================
  Restructures the Recharge Affinity portal's default "Your next order" card
  to match the Figma design (762:6635 desktop / 762:6327 mobile).

  Strategy:
  - JS MutationObserver detects when Recharge renders the card, then
    marks DOM sections with [data-cf-*] attributes and physically moves
    the button container to the bottom of the card.
  - CSS targets [data-cf-*] attributes for layout, typography, and visibility.
  - If JS fails, Recharge's native styles still render (graceful degradation).
{% endcomment %}

